y be related to the differential duration of lactation and maternal care periods, as the breeding cycle in Desmodus is longer than in Diphylla. The average time of reaching maturity: epiphysis closure of wing bones, adult weight, scrotal testes, and first pregnancy, as well as the first flight time and the time when males begin to roost apart from the principal colony, were later in Desmodus than in Diphylla. The variation between the two genera for duration of ontogeny and maternal care periods may be related to the learning needs for predation on different types of prey.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Delpietro, H.A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Russo, R.G.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/3782b09c1ede712eac284b3ca25eb893", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/a9b7132730f7869f43009139a8eebb8020146262ad6edf01e36d0d4c596a2ecf", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/7BPNGBFW", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/7BPNGBFW", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/79f9720cbef03298074181f8c9f051e6!/b36802-39283", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f496e811a3", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "2", "pages": "65-78", "title": "Mammalian Biology", "volume": "67"}, "alternate_i